# High-Level Overview

## Purpose
The purpose of these Cursor Rules is to guide the AI in generating code for the Friendlines app, a minimalist social newsfeed application. The app aims to keep users updated on their friends' lives through AI-generated newsflash-style headlines.

## Key Objectives
- Ensure code consistency and adherence to the app's design principles.
- Facilitate the creation of modular and reusable components.
- Support AI-powered headline generation with user control.

## Design Principles
- Minimalist and readable interface.
- Fast feedback loops via push notifications.
- Modular, reusable components.

## Structure
The rules are organized by category, feature, and functionality to ensure easy navigation and updates.
